Sentencas: High power density operation is essential for cost reduction in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs), and thus the present work proposes a highly active Gd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-delta (GSC) and Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 (GDC) nanocomposite cathode for intermediate-temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: High-performance Gd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ and Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 nanocomposite cathode for achieving high power density in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Its nanocomposite structure is formed by using GSC-GDC nanocomposite particles synthesized via spray pyrolysis, which produces uniform-sized secondary particles consisting of nano-sized GSC and GDC crystallites.
Titulo: High-performance Gd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ and Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 nanocomposite cathode for achieving high power density in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The resulting cathode has an extensive electrochemically active triple-phase boundary and has electrically conductive networks formed with highly dispersed GSC and GDC crystallites.
Titulo: High-performance Gd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ and Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 nanocomposite cathode for achieving high power density in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the GSC-GDC nanocomposite cathode exhibits a performance comparable to a high-performance Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-delta and Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 nanocomposite cathode.
Titulo: High-performance Gd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ and Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 nanocomposite cathode for achieving high power density in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An anode-supported SOFC with the GSC-GDC nanocomposite cathode achieves remarkably high power densities at 0.75 V, i.e., 3.66, 2.60, 1.66, and 0.98 W cm(-2) at 800, 750, 700, and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: High-performance Gd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ and Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 nanocomposite cathode for achieving high power density in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results suggest the proposed nanocomposite cathode yields a synergistic effect of a high catalytic activity of GSC-GDC and a fine nanocomposite structure, leading to high power density operation of an SOFC.
Titulo: High-performance Gd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ and Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 nanocomposite cathode for achieving high power density in solid oxide fuel cells
